content.text: Natto was a member of the Suna Suna Clan along with Vivi, Koza, Okame, and Kebi.

As a child, he wore an un-buttoned shirt, with black spots near the bottom, and a black stripe at the end of the short sleeves. He wore a sash, with shorts, and sandals. He appears to have a scar above his right eye, and also has black hair and a bandage on his stomach.

As a child, Natto was a loyal member of the Suna Suna Clan and risked his life when Vivi was attacked by Agotogi and his gang. Despite of being over-powered, he and his friends held their ground but lost in the end.
Natto wielded a stick, but he didn't seem to be very good at using it.
When he was a child, he and the other children managed to protect Vivi from Agotogi and his gang of thugs. Despite failing, Koza managed find a way to defeat Agotogi himself.
In the anime, he is not shown with a scar above his right eye.

elements.text: His name comes from a type of Japanese food called Nattō.
↑  One Piece Blue: Grand Data File (p. 76), Natto's name is revealed.
